    {
      "type": "LinguisticObject",
      "content": "The Movement Record turns the claim for Metaconceptual Art into a citable textual work and a machine-readable evidence surface. It distinguishes local validity from external canonization while pointing to Linked Art, Wikidata, Getty vocabularies, IIIF, schema.org, and the git-derived Activity Stream.",
